{"tid":1279401,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"*急救聯署聲明* *First Aid Declaration*","createTime":"2019-07-02T16:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:38:28.000Z","uid":273125,"like":394,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e2f772ea7cb87bb339c0beaa2c49fd5d78594a","tid":1279401,"uid":273125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"我哋係一班自發性開急救站嘅人，自問只係一班愛護香港而想保護家園既護士同急救員。由六月九號開始，我哋已經決定與抗爭者同行。七月一號，我哋有出勤，亦親眼目睹立法會既來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋未必完全同意年輕義士既升級手法，包括塗鴉等等動作，但係我敢保證，大家有咩行動我哋都第一時間企出，盡力保護各位。無論你係咩身分 &mdash; 年輕老幼既抗爭者、義士或靜坐抗議、執勤警察、記者&nbsp; &mdash;&nbsp; 我哋都一定竭盡所能去幫助你地，做好後勤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，但係請體諒我哋團隊都係人，分身不暇，未必能夠即時照顧在場所有有需要嘅人。希望黎緊既抗爭行動入面，唔會再見到流血，唔會再見到有人犧牲任何野，因為真心一個都不能少。香港靠我哋每個人去捍衛，但係照顧好自己先可以照顧到其他人！勿切勉強自己！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位抗爭者，無論你係用咩方法去抗爭，我哋都支持你！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋一齊出嚟，一齊返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of first aiders that have been there since the first protest on the 9th of June. We are voluntary and are made up of people with first aid experience nurses and doctors. We were present on the 1st of July to witness what happened to at the Legislative Council.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe do not condone the use of violence and vandalism by the protesters the young generation Hong Kong, however we are there to fully support the movement and any subsequent actions taken by our fellow Hong Kongers.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhether you are young or old, police or press or protester, whether you vandalised or whether you have sat peacefully. We will be there as first responders. We will try our best to help you and get you to safety.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe may not agree with the methods of our brothers and sisters, but we will be watching over everyone.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe come out together. We go home together."},{"pid":"4251ddb532375a8da7a368e34d203f83688543cc","tid":1279401,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de71ae5f88b36635ce3fbe924c83580d6ebfe40f","tid":1279401,"uid":246243,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"點都好...保護好自己...著合適嘅嘢先去合適地方...咩都無嘅去番後啲幫手...處理過...好多受傷其實早一步著合適嘅嘢就可以保護到自己避免受傷"},{"pid":"c4800654554bccf677693b12211874a35ac4c0ea","tid":1279401,"uid":50901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"多謝你地"},{"pid":"8dcde9e00c52be0c90b6a27f8d316f38c35b592b","tid":1279401,"uid":273182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1e2f772ea7cb87bb339c0beaa2c49fd5d78594a","tid":1279401,"uid":273125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"我哋係一班自發性開急救站嘅人，自問只係一班愛護香港而想保護家園既護士同急救員。由六月九號開始，我哋已經決定與抗爭者同行。七月一號，我哋有出勤，亦親眼目睹立法會既來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋未必完全同意年輕義士既升級手法，包括塗鴉等等動作，但係我敢保證，大家有咩行動我哋都第一時間企出，盡力保護各位。無論你係咩身分 &mdash; 年輕老幼既抗爭者、義士或靜坐抗議、執勤警察、記者&nbsp; &mdash;&nbsp; 我哋都一定竭盡所能去幫助你地，做好後勤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，但係請體諒我哋團隊都係人，分身不暇，未必能夠即時照顧在場所有有需要嘅人。希望黎緊既抗爭行動入面，唔會再見到流血，唔會再見到有人犧牲任何野，因為真心一個都不能少。香港靠我哋每個人去捍衛，但係照顧好自己先可以照顧到其他人！勿切勉強自己！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位抗爭者，無論你係用咩方法去抗爭，我哋都支持你！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋一齊出嚟，一齊返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of first aiders that have been there since the first protest on the 9th of June. We are voluntary and are made up of people with first aid experience nurses and doctors. We were present on the 1st of July to witness what happened to at the Legislative Council.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe do not condone the use of violence and vandalism by the protesters the young generation Hong Kong, however we are there to fully support the movement and any subsequent actions taken by our fellow Hong Kongers.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhether you are young or old, police or press or protester, whether you vandalised or whether you have sat peacefully. We will be there as first responders. We will try our best to help you and get you to safety.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe may not agree with the methods of our brothers and sisters, but we will be watching over everyone.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe come out together. We go home together."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc069a8d28c9013db2b05502ac44e8e691f536e6","tid":1279401,"uid":207967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1e2f772ea7cb87bb339c0beaa2c49fd5d78594a","tid":1279401,"uid":273125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"我哋係一班自發性開急救站嘅人，自問只係一班愛護香港而想保護家園既護士同急救員。由六月九號開始，我哋已經決定與抗爭者同行。七月一號，我哋有出勤，亦親眼目睹立法會既來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋未必完全同意年輕義士既升級手法，包括塗鴉等等動作，但係我敢保證，大家有咩行動我哋都第一時間企出，盡力保護各位。無論你係咩身分 &mdash; 年輕老幼既抗爭者、義士或靜坐抗議、執勤警察、記者&nbsp; &mdash;&nbsp; 我哋都一定竭盡所能去幫助你地，做好後勤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，但係請體諒我哋團隊都係人，分身不暇，未必能夠即時照顧在場所有有需要嘅人。希望黎緊既抗爭行動入面，唔會再見到流血，唔會再見到有人犧牲任何野，因為真心一個都不能少。香港靠我哋每個人去捍衛，但係照顧好自己先可以照顧到其他人！勿切勉強自己！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位抗爭者，無論你係用咩方法去抗爭，我哋都支持你！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋一齊出嚟，一齊返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of first aiders that have been there since the first protest on the 9th of June. We are voluntary and are made up of people with first aid experience nurses and doctors. We were present on the 1st of July to witness what happened to at the Legislative Council.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe do not condone the use of violence and vandalism by the protesters the young generation Hong Kong, however we are there to fully support the movement and any subsequent actions taken by our fellow Hong Kongers.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhether you are young or old, police or press or protester, whether you vandalised or whether you have sat peacefully. We will be there as first responders. We will try our best to help you and get you to safety.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe may not agree with the methods of our brothers and sisters, but we will be watching over everyone.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe come out together. We go home together."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"感謝你哋連日嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1860233913066fdf30755f519c8f1f6bc33f03ed","tid":1279401,"uid":109668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0354e50d7b58c4a5fa554660a322e84b4da94905","tid":1279401,"uid":229028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4de5738ae0afe00b8feeef3f8da4cfe35912099","tid":1279401,"uid":252193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2595835526216595e9dd2a948b3741e3b48e1682","tid":1279401,"uid":42135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"多謝你地"},{"pid":"83316f367d7af3b86d8a323c8c981015d98c5b95","tid":1279401,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb691cce5c1cbd4261f86468eb061a9bc1a31977","tid":1279401,"uid":39717,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"都係果句：講清楚邊度要first aid<br />\n同埋唔好煲底要first aid 嗌到出海富<br />\n我個裝備重，跑幾次其實幾金<br />\n仲要去到已經有廿個first aider 係度<br />\n<br />\n雖然食好多次炸糊，但我依然會繼續跑，至多跑得慢左架啫<br />\n<br />\n大家加油呀！"},{"pid":"fc28d508035c987298264480c10a45cd33e839da","tid":1279401,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"希望生性啲唔好再黎肉盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be55134297899562a5c48d5f71d3cc1ef11002c4","tid":1279401,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"Thanks you for all your 